data.description: MOVE IN READY! THIS BEAUTIFUL LAKE WALES HOME IS PRICED TO SELL QUICKLY, ALLOWING YOU TO MAXIMIZE YOUR EQUITY! This spacious property boasts a 3BR/2BA/2 Car garage. Situated on an oversized lot spanning .39 acres, it offers a sense of privacy with no rear neighbors. The home spans over 1,500+ square feet and features a NEW ROOF installed in 2021, ensuring peace of mind for the future. As you step inside, you'll be greeted by a modern and stylish interior. The kitchen is a true highlight, with stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, tile backsplash, a large convenient breakfast bar, and ample cabinet space for all your culinary needs. The master bedroom is a tranquil retreat with its own en-suite bathroom, providing a private oasis within the home. Natural light floods the living spaces through two sliding glass doors that lead out to the screened-in patio, offering the perfect spot to relax or entertain guests. As you explore the backyard, you'll discover a mature avocado tree, adding a touch of natural beauty to the outdoor space. The home is located on a peaceful cul-de-sac, providing a serene and quiet setting. Do not miss the opportunity to make this Lake Wales home your own. With its modern features, spacious layout, and charming backyard, it offers the perfect blend of comfort and tranquility. Conveniently located. Close to shopping and restaurants. Schedule your showing today and envision the possibilities of calling this place your HOME SWEET HOME! **PLEASE NOTE NO LEASING OR RENTING ALLOWED PER HOA**
